<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Masterpiece - 포토부스</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard/dist/web/static/pretendard.css');
        
        :root {
            --primary: #2D3250;
            --secondary: #424769;
            --background: #0F111A;
            --surface: #161823;
            --text: #FFFFFF;
            --text-secondary: #B3B3B3;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: var(--background);
            color: var(--text);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--background) 100%);
        }
        
        .hero-content {
            max-width: 800px;
        }
        
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
        
        .btn-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid var(--primary);
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 2px solid var(--primary);
        }
        
        .footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: var(--surface);
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }
            
            .hero p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
            
            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            .btn-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Masterpiece</h1>
            <p>소중한 순간을 담는 포토부스</p>
            <div class="btn-container">
                <a href="/promotion" class="btn btn-primary">갤러리 보기</a>
                <a href="/admin" class="btn btn-secondary">관리자 페이지</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>© 2024 Masterpiece. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 